From ebc1a98be713491fc20a6c8a98b2f88647f5e191 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Date: Thu, 8 May 2025 15:12:55 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: cfg: build ax210 family FW names dynamically
Git-commit: ebc1a98be713491fc20a6c8a98b2f88647f5e191
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

Add support for the TY MAC (discrete device) and GF4 RF to
the list of MAC/RF types, and use that to remove fw_name_pre
for the ax210 family devices.

Signed-off-by: Johannes Berg <johannes.berg@intel.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250508121306.1277801-5-miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com
Signed-off-by: Miri Korenblit <miriam.rachel.korenblit@intel.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
